Module org.example.proyecto
Package org.example.proyecto.model.hotel

Class HotelDTO

java.lang.Object
org.example.proyecto.model.housing.HousingDTO
org.example.proyecto.model.hotel.HotelDTO
public class HotelDTO extends HousingDTO
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for hotel information. This class extends the HousingDTO class and represents hotel-specific data, including hotel classification, room type, and host number.
Since:
2024-05-28
